SOLICITATION NUMBER: RFQ-SEC-2026-001

AGENCY: Department of Homeland Infrastructure

PROJECT TITLE: Federal Building Security Services

1. Scope of Work
The contractor shall provide physical security services for a federal office building located in Washington, DC.

2. Requirements

2.1 Personnel
- Minimum of 5 armed security guards
- All personnel must possess active state security licenses
- Background checks required

2.2 Experience
- Minimum 3 years of experience providing security services
- At least 2 prior federal or municipal contracts

2.3 Equipment
- CCTV monitoring capability
- Radio communication systems

2.4 Compliance
- Must comply with FAR regulations
- Must be registered in SAM.gov
- Must meet Small Business set-aside requirements

3. Performance Period
Base year with two 1-year option periods.

4. Submission Deadline
March 30, 2026